nodes.text: Star Wars: Build Your Own X-Wing 1
Star Wars: Build Your Own X-Wing 1 is the first issue of the Star Wars: Build Your Own X-Wing published by De Agostini.
Cockpit canopy frame, upper starboard laser cannon housing and barrel parts, R2-D2 head, body, lighting effect and leg parts.
